in LICENSE.

This adaptation changes the product target from Claude CLI usage to Codex
usage. Major changes include:

- reading Codex rollout logs from ~/.codex/sessions and archived_sessions
- aggregating Codex token_count events by day, week, month, model, and tool
- estimating API value from public model pricing
- reading Codex app-server account usage and rate-limit summaries
- displaying available manual reset credits and earliest available credit expiry
- adding Codex-oriented profile stats, theme switching, screenshot capture,
  and macOS multi-monitor / notched-display popover positioning fixes

